.IP "\(bu" 2
Check the magic and version numbers in log files when first opening them\&.
.IP "\(bu" 2
Fix a bug with cache leaf size accounting for statistics\&. refs \fCWT-1885\fP, \fCWT-1919\fP
.IP "\(bu" 2
Fix a bug where checkpoint could skip a page that was rewritten in memory\&. refs \fCWT-1946\fP
.IP "\(bu" 2
