Fix a bug in handle close where we could fail to clear the open handle flag\&. refs \fCWT-1915\fP
.IP "\(bu" 2
Fix a bug in in-memory splits, don't allow any other eviction of a page if the page is being split\&. refs \fCWT-1916\fP, \fCWT-1917\fP
