Save the wiredtiger_open configuration when a database is created, so that settings like cache size, extensions and logging are set consistently by all subsequent users of the database\&.
.PP
Add an \fC--enable-verbose\fP option to configure\&. In order to access the verbose message functionality available as part of the wiredtiger_open and \fBWT_CONNECTION::reconfigure\fP APIs, it is necessary to pass the \fC--enable-verbose\fP option to configure\&.
